===Derivation===
[[mammary]] (adj.) + [[gland]]

===Noun===
'''mammary gland''' (''plural:'' [[mammary]] [[glands]])
# Gland that becomes active on most mammals just before childbirth and remains active for varying lengths of time during infancy of offspring.  Expresses milk for infant sustenance.  Syn. [[breast]], [[udder]], [[boob]], [[tit]], [[dug]].

